  "title": "Linear and rotation - rolling without friction",
  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a disk of radius R that is moving horizontally to the right on a flat surface with a speed labeled v, while rotating clockwise with an angular velocity labeled omega.\" src=\"/images/57dacaf928c4da9a93d8c235978677a1.svg\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A disk of radius <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"R\"><math alttext=\"R\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>R</mi></math></span></span> moves with negligible friction along a horizontal surface with a translational velocity <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"v\"><math alttext=\"v\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>v</mi></math></span></span> as it rotates with an angular velocity <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"omega\"><math alttext=\"omega\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>ω</mi></math></span></span>. Which of the following statements must be true regarding the angular velocity of the disk?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i4",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"omega equals the fraction v over R\"><math alttext=\"omega equals the fraction v over R\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mi>ω</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>v</mi><mi>R</mi></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"omega is less than the fraction v over R\"><math alttext=\"omega is less than the fraction v over R\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mi>ω</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mfrac><mi>v</mi><mi>R</mi></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"omega is greater than the fraction v over R\"><math alttext=\"omega is greater than the fraction v over R\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mi>ω</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mfrac><mi>v</mi><mi>R</mi></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">A relationship cannot be determined for <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"omega\"><math alttext=\"omega\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>ω</mi></math></span></span> in terms of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"v\"><math alttext=\"v\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>v</mi></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"R\"><math alttext=\"R\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>R</mi></math></span></span>.</p>",
        "value": "i4"
      }
